Adverse event cost parameters

Source: R/data.R
params_costs_ae.Rd

Mean costs by adverse event.

params_costs_ae

Format

A data table with the following columns:

ae_name

Name of the adverse event.

ae_abb

Abbreviation for the adverse event.

mean

Mean costs.

lower

2.5% quantile for mean costs. Currently assumed to be +20% of mean costs given lack of data for estimating standard errors.

upper

97.5% quantile for mean costs. Currently assumed to be -20% of mean costs given lack of data for estimating standard errors.

se

Standard error of costs.

ref

Reference for mean costs.
